Preheat broiler. Position oven rack approximately 6 inches from heat source. Spread butter on one side of each slice of bread. Spread peanut butter on unbuttered side of 8 slices of bread, jelly on the other 8, and combine to make 8 sandwiches. Arrange all 8 sandwiches on a baking sheet. Broil sandwiches 2 to 3 minutes on each side, or until lightly browned.